programme.title: Bidadari: Merah Gaun Pengantin Ep13
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Almy bertemu pemuda kaya yang sombong bernama Heykal yang belajar di kolej yang sama dengannya. Almy berkawan baik dengan Faisal dan Nadia hingga terperangkap dengan cinta tiga segi. Masa sama Almy menjalin hubungan baik dengan Datin Balqis yang mengagumi bakatnya dalam bidang perunding perkahwinan. Datin Balqis menawarkan Almy menjadi perunding perkahwinan untuk anaknya, Heykal dengan Suzie. Pada mulanya Almy menolak tetapi akhinya dia berubah fikiran. Heykal menyesal dengan sikap sombongnya terhadap Almy dan akhirnya jatuh cinta. Masa yang sama Almy pula jatuh cinta dengan Faisal. Siapakah jejaka yang menjadi pilihan Almy? Pelakon: Syafiq Kyle, Nad Zainal, Fazreen Rafi, Falisha Crossley, Syed Ali, Faye Kusairi, Mimi Ernida, Alif Hadi, Nor Albaniah, Norlia Ghani, Rahim Omar, Mubarak Majid, dan Raja Ema.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Kisah 1 Rumah Ep3
programme.desc: Drama kehidupan yang mengisahkan Ika yang bekerja di sebuah caf serta Shira merupakan penyewa bilik di sebuah rumah kedai. Pada satu hari, pasangan bernama Suhaidi dan isterinya Wulan telah datang ke rumah tersebut untuk menyewa rumah mereka. Ika dan Elyn memujuk Shikin agar Shira bekerja di kafenya tetapi emak Shikin meminta shira selesaikan masalahnya bersama bekas suaminya dahulu. Rumah sewa mereka bersepah! Puan Asiah upah tukang cuci untuk bersihkan rumah dan memberi amaran kepada penghuni rumah tersebut. Pelakon: Nur Risteena Munir, Natasya Elyza, Abon, Raja Ema, Najwa Nasir, Kishvin, Jasmin Hamid, Hadi Tahir, Aninth Aqila, Aliff Hadi, Nur Natasya Mahyan, Zaidi Omar, Aziz M. Osman, dan Cico.

programme.title: Inovasi Untuk Rakyat Ep24
programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang memaparkan maklumat mengenai inovasi teknologi maklumat dalam perkhidmatan awam di negara kita. Program majalah ini merangkumi segmen Sepintas Bersama, Testimoni Pengguna dan Sketsa Rakyat, turut menjemput individu yang terlibat secara langsung bagi berkongsi pencerahan berkenaan agensi yang ditampilkan. Kementerian Pendidikan Malaysia memperkenalkan UPU Online dan aplikasi UPU Pocket bagi memudahkan permohonan kemasukan ke institusi pengajian tinggi. Sistem ini membolehkan pelajar membuat semakan dan permohonan dengan lebih pantas dan mesra pengguna. Maklumat lanjut boleh dilayari di http://online.moe.gov.my.

programme.title: Spektra: Saat Aku Berpaling Ep8
programme.desc: 13 tahun berlalu, tiba-tiba Hisham kembali bersama anaknya, Faizal ke rumah Saudi. Namun, pertanyaan bertubi-tubi daripada Saudi tentang Rosnah, Farid dan Faizah mengundang kemarahan dan mengganggu emosi Hisham. Apa sebenarnya berlaku? Walaupun berat, terpaksa Lia menerima lamaran keluarga Azram demi untuk menyelamatkan ayahnya dan syarikat. Hajat Hashim tertunai apabila anak-anak Rosnah pulang bertemunya. Sikap tidak sabar Azram makin merimaskan Dato' Razif. programme.title: Ekspresi Eko Ep10
programme.desc: Program majalah bertemakan perlancongan yang memberikan fokus kepada ecotourism atau perlancongan eko yang terdapat dalam 12 negeri di seluruh Malaysia. programme.title: Bro, Nampak Motor Gua?
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Epol, seorang pemuda yang sangat menyayangi motosikalnya hasil titik peluh sendiri. Namun, motosikal kesayangannya itu telah dicuri oleh dua perompak. Dalam usaha mencari motosikalnya, Epol bertemu dengan Azura, seorang peguam yang juga menjadi mangsa perompak yang sama apabila beg tangannya diragut. Tanpa disedari, dalam beg tangan Azura terdapat sebuah pemacu USB yang mengandungi dokumen penting milik Tan Sri Bakhir, seorang ahli perniagaan kaya. Tan Sri Bakhir menawarkan ganjaran RM50,000 kepada Epol sekiranya dia berjaya mendapatkan semula pemacu USB tersebut dan menyerahkannya kepada pihak bank. Dengan semangat dan keazaman, Epol memulakan pengembaraan penuh aksi dan komedi untuk menjejaki perompak tersebut demi mendapatkan semula motosikalnya dan pemacu USB itu.

Dalam keadaan huru-hara ini, Adif pulang dari KLIA dan mendapati ibu bapanya telah meninggal dalam kemalangan. Kini, Adif menjadi penaung syarikat yang dulunya milik Idris dan memaksa mak mentua dan bapa mentuanya keluar dari rumah banglo mereka dalam masa dua hari. Rian marah dan tidak dapat menerima tindakan Adif. Adif menerangkan bahawa dia telah mengambil alih syarikat Waris Putra. Rian yang kini di wad, dan baru tahu yang dia mengandung, tidak mahu Adif di sisinya dan lebih memerlukan mama dan papanya.

programme.desc: Rodi diburu polis selepas membunuh Rajoo demi menyelamatkan ibunya, Juita, yang akhirnya terbunuh. Kesnya jadi sensasi media, mengangkat isu ketidakadilan sosial terhadap anak jalanan seperti Kasyorga.

programme.title: Ganjil Ep5
programme.desc: Dunia mimpi tidak lagi menjadi tempat yang menenangkan, manakala dunia nyata terasa lebih menakutkan. Nabila dan Amry mula tertanya-tanya sama ada takdir sedang mempermainkan mereka dengan kejam.

programme.title: Blood Karma
programme.desc: Dalam perjalanan pulang setelah bertahun-tahun belajar di luar negara, seorang ahli farmasi yang bersikap terbuka mula terhalang oleh tanggungjawab sebagai anak terhadap keluarganya yang taksub dengan kepercayaan karut, serta satu siri pembunuhan misteri yang berlaku di rumah tersebut.

programme.title: SAM
programme.desc: Sam, yang pernah menjalinkan hubungan intim dengan rakan sekerjanya, mendapati bahawa bukan dirinya sahaja yang menyukai Lisa. Suatu hari, Lisa telah diculik dan Sam bertekad untuk menyelamatkan Lisa serta mencari dalang di sebalik penculikan itu tanpa menyedari bahawa perkara itu akan mengubah hidupnya selama-lamanya.

programme.title: KL Zombie
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nipis, seorang pemalas yang menjadi wira tanpa rela apabila wabak zombi merampas satu-satunya kehidupan yang dikenalnya.

programme.title: Model Family Ep4
programme.desc: Sebuah keluarga ibu bapa tunggal (Yu Xiang dan Tong Tong) berpindah ke kawasan kejiranan baharu di mana kehidupan semua orang nampak sempurna. Walau bagaimanapun, keadaan mungkin kelihatan cerah di luar, rahsia gelap dan seram menyerbu setiap keluarga dari dalam, dan tidak ada yang benar-benar seperti yang kelihatan.

programme.title: Filler
programme.desc: Filler

programme.title: Evolusi KL Drift
programme.desc: Zack dan Sham adalah dua nama yang sinonim dengan istilah keakraban. Hubungan sebagai dua sahabat karib yang sama-sama berkongsi hobi dan minat dalam bidang perlumbaan kereta 'drift'.

programme.title: The Perished
programme.desc: Menghadapi penamatan kehamilan di Ireland merupakan sesuatu yang sukar bagi Sarah Dekker. Disisihkan oleh keluarganya yang fanatik agama dan selepas putus cinta dengan teman lelakinya yang tidak berbelas kasihan, dia pergi ke rumah seorang rakan yang bersimpati di kawasan pedalaman untuk memulihkan diri. Namun tanpa pengetahuannya, rumah lama itu terletak di atas kubur besar bayi-bayi yang tidak diingini dan roh mereka yang hilang serta keliru mahu dilahirkan semula. Berbekalkan rasa bersalah dan penyesalan, roh-roh itu memerlukan seorang ibu. Dan mereka mungkin telah menemuinya dalam diri Sarah.

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga EP5 Ep5
programme.desc: Rodi diburu polis selepas membunuh Rajoo demi menyelamatkan ibunya, Juita, yang akhirnya terbunuh. Kesnya jadi sensasi media, mengangkat isu ketidakadilan sosial terhadap anak jalanan seperti Kasyorga.

programme.title: Vengeance Of An Assasin
programme.desc: The Assassins' Code Patuhi misi. Jangan alihkan pandangan dari sasaran. Jangan tunjukkan belas kasihan. Natee (Dan Chupong) menjadi pembunuh untuk mencari tahu siapa yang membunuh ibu bapanya. Ketika dia semakin hampir membongkar rangkaian rahsia kuasa dan korupsi, dia dikhianati dalam satu tugas, menjadikannya sasaran dan membahayakan orang yang disayanginya. Kini, dikhianati dan diburu oleh pembunuh paling berbahaya, Natee mengikut kod baru Jadi lebih pantas, lebih kuat, serang lebih ganas, dan bertahan hidup. Filem ini diarahkan oleh Panna Rittikrai, koreografer aksi Ong Bak dan mentor kepada bintang aksi Tony Jaa, yang kembali bekerjasama dengan Dan Chupong dari filem Born to Fight (2004) dalam filem terakhirnya.

programme.title: Hitman
programme.desc: Komrad Tanthai (Chatchai Plengpanich), seorang pembunuh upahan terkenal dan sangat profesional, menerima tugasan baharu daripada Chaba (Bongkuch Kongmalai), bekas kekasih ketua mafia berpangkat tinggi, Wong (Thanit Jatanukul). Tugasan tersebut adalah untuk mencari dan membunuh ketua pengedar dadah dan 'Godfather' Chinatown, Leemeng (Nirud Sirijanya). Kematian Leemeng mencetuskan konflik antara kumpulan mafia rasmi dan tidak rasmi. Kini, semua orang memburu Tanthai tanpa mengira apa jua harganya.

programme.title: Blood Karma
programme.desc: Dalam perjalanan pulang setelah bertahun-tahun belajar di luar negara, seorang ahli farmasi yang bersikap terbuka mula terhalang oleh tanggungjawab sebagai anak terhadap keluarganya yang taksub dengan kepercayaan karut, serta satu siri pembunuhan misteri yang berlaku di rumah tersebut.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep8
programme.desc: Imran membunuh Ajeeb dan Uzair bersumpah untuk membalas dendam. Tanpa berfikir panjang Hatta mahu segera menyerang Imran tetapi Uzair mahu memastikan rakan-rakannya selamat. Ashikin merayu agar Imran menghentikan dendamnya terhadap Uzair. Apabila Imran menculik Noramina, bermulalah pertarungan terakhir.

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga EP5 Ep5
programme.desc: Rodi diburu polis selepas membunuh Rajoo demi menyelamatkan ibunya, Juita, yang akhirnya terbunuh. Kesnya jadi sensasi media, mengangkat isu ketidakadilan sosial terhadap anak jalanan seperti Kasyorga.

programme.title: Black Ep6
programme.desc: Di Seri Setia, Black dan Sofia bekerjasama untuk menghalang satu pembunuhan yang berpotensi untuk berlaku. Semasa berada di sana, Black terimbas kembali masa lalu Malik, satu fenomena yang membingungkannya. Pemergian mereka ini juga merupakan titik perubahan cara Sofia melihat keupayaannya. Kesanggupan Sofia menggadaikan nyawanya untuk menyelamatkan nyawa orang lain memperbaharui tanggapan Black terhadapnya. Adakah cinta mula berputik? Black tertarik dan pada masa yang sama bingung dengan perasaannya terhadap Sofia, satu perasaan yang asing buat Black, seorang yang mementingkan diri. Tetapi hari yang bersinar menjadi pudar apabila Black kembali ke rumah dan mendapati bilik tersembunyi Malik telah digeledah dan dikosongkan. Sementara itu, pembunuh upahan telah meragut nyawa seorang lagi mangsa dan Detektif Borhan mendapati kematian itu ada kaitan dengan pembunuhan Nurul Najwa.

programme.title: Syaitan Munafik
programme.desc: Sekumpulan anak muda yang gemarkan dunia yang sofistikated cuba mencari rakan-rakan mereka yang telah hilang di sebuah rumah berhantu lima tahun lalu.

programme.title: Penghujung Jalan
programme.desc: Mastura, seorang wanita muda yang terlanjur cinta, terpaksa menanggung akibat apabila hamil luar nikah. Selepas melahirkan, dia nekad meninggalkan bayinya di hadapan rumah Aina dan Rosli, pasangan suami isteri yang masih meratapi kehilangan anak akibat keguguran. Kehadiran bayi itu seolah-olah menghidupkan semula harapan mereka untuk menjadi ibu bapa. Namun, apabila pihak berkuasa campur tangan demi siasatan, bayi itu terpaksa diambil semula. Hal ini meninggalkan Aina dalam kesedihan yang mendalam, sekali lagi kehilangan sesuatu yang sangat berharga.

programme.title: Sayang
programme.desc: Pelajar kolej swasta, Noni sering dikawal ketat oleh abangnya, Herman dan tidak boleh keluar bersosial seperti temannya yang lain. Herman mula bertindak menjadi ketua keluarga setelah kematian bapa mereka setahun yang lalu. Noni menghadiri satu majlis hari jadi dan terjadi sesuatu yang membuatkan Herman semakin ketat mengawal gerak geri Noni.

programme.title: Ilhamku
programme.desc: Sham, seorang lelaki weirdo yang kreatif dan gemar menghadapi cabaran, bersetuju menjadi juri bagi sebuah uji bakat atas permintaan sahabatnya, Shima. Di situlah dia bertemu dengan Noreen, seorang penyanyi baharu yang berbakat namun bermasalah. Meskipun Noreen sering menimbulkan pelbagai masalah di syarikat rakaman kerana sikap tidak berdisiplinnya, Sham yang jatuh hati padanya sentiasa memaafkan segala kesilapannya. Namun, kasih sayang tanpa batas itu akhirnya memakan diri apabila Noreen semakin angkuh dan mula mempergunakan Sham demi kepentingan peribadinya.

programme.title: Da Di Du
programme.desc: Badu, Badi dan Bada, bertemu dan menjadi sahabat ketika mempelajari ilmu persilatan dengan seorang guru persilatan bernama Pak Tua kerana ingin memperbetulkan kisah silam yang tidak menyebelahi nasib mereka. Sepanjang itu terdapat pelbagai peristiwa yang berlaku dari mula mereka belajar sehingga tamat dan pulang ke kampung masing-masing untuk memperbetulkan masa lalu mereka.

programme.title: Kemarau Panjang
programme.desc: Berlatarbelakangkan zaman darurat 19481960, Kampung Hulu menjadi sasaran ancaman komunis yang semakin menggugat keamanan penduduk. Demi mempertahankan keselamatan, pihak British berusaha menubuhkan pasukan Home Guard. Namun, dalam kekalutan yang melanda, muncul beberapa pengkhianat yang menjadi tali barut komunis, lantas mencetuskan kekacauan dan ketegangan yang kian meruncing dalam komuniti kampung itu.

programme.title: Sayang Salmah
programme.desc: Semangat cinta akan bangsa dan negara diterapkan dalam diri Hassan dan Salleh selaku anak kepada Encik Jabar dan Dasimah yang inginkan anak mereka mempunyai rasa patriotik akan negara. Hassan, aktif dalam bidang politik manakala Salleh menjadi seorang pemuda liar yang suka berhibur. Segalanya berubah apabila ayah mereka meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Teruna Idaman
programme.desc: Leha, seorang gadis lincah dan berdikari, sering menolak pinangan yang diatur ibunya. Alasannya mudah dia belum bersedia dan belum bertemu jejaka idaman. Setiap kali ada rombongan merisik, Leha rela berpura-pura kurang siuman semata-mata mahu menggagalkan rancangan perkahwinan itu. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila Tengku Iskandar, seorang pegawai baharu yang kacak dan berkarisma, muncul di tempat kerjanya. Buat pertama kali, hati Leha mula terusik. Demi menarik perhatian Iskandar, Leha sanggup lakukan apa saja termasuk mengorbankan wang simpanannya. Tapi adakah cinta berbalas, atau sekadar angan-angan?

programme.title: Merah
programme.desc: Pilihan antara baik atau buruk menentukan di mana pengakhiran jalan kisah hidup Merah. Terpaksa menjalani hukuman penjara akibat pilihan yang dibuatnya, Merah bertemu seseorang yang istimewa. Kasih, seorang kaunselor menemui Merah. Namun, ada rahsia yang disimpan erat oleh Kasih. Meskipun menyukai antara satu sama lain, pelbagai halangan terpaksa mereka tempuhi bersama.

programme.title: Penghujung Jalan
programme.desc: Mastura, seorang wanita muda yang terlanjur cinta, terpaksa menanggung akibat apabila hamil luar nikah. Hal ini meninggalkan Aina dalam kesedihan yang mendalam, sekali lagi kehilangan sesuatu yang sangat berharga.

programme.title: Gadis Hitam Putih
programme.desc: Kota Jakarta telah digemparkan dengan berita kejadian lebih 20 tahun lalu. Dalam satu perbicaraan di mahkamah, seorang jururawat bernama Mira mengaku telah menukar bayi dua keluarga yang mempunyai latar belakang yang berbeza. Mira bertindak sebegitu kerana dia ingin membalas dendam terhadap seorang doktor yang memutuskan cintanya kerana perbezaan darjat keturunan.

programme.title: Namaku Yassin
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Yanto, seorang penjual jagung bakar yang menjalani kehidupan sederhana di kampung. Segalanya berubah apabila dia bertemu semula dengan sahabat lamanya, Budi, yang baru pulang setelah beberapa tahun bekerja di Malaysia. Terkesima dengan kejayaan Budi, Yanto menerima pelawaan untuk turut sama mengubah nasibnya di Kuala Lumpur. Menggunakan nama samaran "Yassin", dia bekerja sebagai buruh di tapak pembinaan dan bersahabat dengan Mahmud. Di sebalik cabaran hidup di kota, Yassin turut menemui cinta dalam diri Liza, seorang pengurus di tempat kerjanya. Namun, perjalanan mencari rezeki dan erti kehidupan ini tidak semudah yang disangka.

programme.desc: Aura 34 Babe Angels Bikin Hati Semrawutmengisahkan Kevin yang diselamatkan oleh tiga gadis hebat Juleha, Nisa dan Mala ketika diserang di Bali. programme.title: My Heart Ep7
programme.desc: Raisa yang patah hati selepas tunangnya, Rio, hilang tiba-tiba, pergi ke Jakarta untuk mencari jawapan. programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep285
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

The elder, Kai-Teng Chiao, a former athlete turned plumber, gave up his dreams to support his family and finds unexpected healing through a connection with a distant, cold-hearted prosecutor. Meanwhile, the younger, Hsi-Ming Chiao, a successful lawyer, is forced to confront the painful past he buried, which includes his breakup and his fathers suicide, when he meets Pao-Chi Hsu, the woman who holds the key to the memories he lost a decade ago.

programme.title: The Hedgehog
programme.desc: Wang's odd behaviour and quirky ideas make him a social outcast. His teenage nephew Zhou, who is ashamed of his stutter, becomes Wang's only friend. Together, these misfits challenge traditional family expectations and social misunderstandings, supporting and inspiring each other as they seek their own paths in life.

programme.title: Love at First Lie
programme.desc: An ordinary, cheerful and kind-hearted girl Bao, meets a troubled rich guy Edward by chance one summer. To ruin his fathers remarriage plans, Edward hires Bao and her friend to sabotage the wedding and that is how Bao and Edward meet and fall in love. All seems well for the sweet couple until their love quickly takes an unexpected turn

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartels turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brothers hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protg Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: Go for Broke
programme.desc: A ruthless drug trafficking group has destroyed countless families due to drug addiction, including Zhang Yao's family. Vowing to take revenge, Zhang Yao teams up with Detective An to take down the drug lords. As their revenge plot unfolds, do they share a common foe or harbour personal agendas?

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home; an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death; the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: May Who?
programme.desc: The story is about a super standard girl in school, May Who, is on a quest to win the love of a school senior heart-throbber, Fame, with her new-found friend, Pong. The only secret is that she can discharge electricity when she gets excited

programme.title: Born to Fly
programme.desc: Lei Yu has officially become the new generation of Chinese test pilots after rounds of strict selection. Captain Zhang Ting leads Lei Yu and other pilots to test the latest fighter jets. Lei Yu keeps pushing the limits in each test flight in the hope of coming up with the perfect plane to ensure the safety of the fighter pilots.

programme.title: HK Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her teams performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night. Lee runs into her ex-boyfriend before a big commercial shoot and drowns her sorrows drinking at Lan Kwai Fong, but finally picks herself up with Chans help.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Chois actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: The Moon Thieves
programme.desc: A crooked watch dealer assembles a daring crew - a thief, an explosive expert, a lock breaker and a watch connoisseur - to steal three luxury watches in Tokyo. Their mission takes an unexpected turn when they discover the legendary 'Moonwatch.' Pursued by the yakuza, the team must unite to navigate the chaos and pull off their high-stakes heist.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau II
programme.desc: Mark, the chief accountant of a money-laundering syndicate, has stolen US$15 billion from the fund and absconded to Thailand with his daughter. Interpol agent Lok seeks help from Ken, the God of Gamblers, to capture the syndicates mastermind. As they search for Mark to testify in the case, Ken reunites with the love of his life

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident

programme.title: Echoes of the Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: Wish Comes True
programme.desc: Xiao Fei is a cheerful girl who has been abandoned by her mother. One day, she encounters a gifted young man named Zi Wai, who is battling a rare disease. Determined to help him, she embarks on a journey to find his lost love. Even when they discover that the drug treating Wai is ineffective, they choose to embrace hope and love together.

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the other's parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents' first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: Marriage With A Liar
programme.desc: Kiki and her boyfriend of seven years, Sean, are to be married in a week but both cheated on each other three days before the wedding. Faced with each of their perfect partners, Kiki and Sean ignore their responsibilities to each other and choose to go their separate ways

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Rus financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the clients data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: The Invisible Guest
programme.desc: Young and beautiful entrepreneur Joanna is a prime suspect in a locked-room murder where her lover is found dead. She pays off a police officer to prove her innocence. During the investigation, they discover another murder case involving Joanna and her lover, and eventually reveals the truth.

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are gambling addicts who have come across each other a few times at the casino, but do not leave impression on each other until they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau. They find themselves falling in love, and decide to get married when they come back to Hong Kong.

programme.title: Happy Dragons
programme.desc: Four retired secret agents embark on a quest for the "Golden Relic" triggered by a mahjong game. Their journey unexpectedly transports them back 30 years, restoring their youth. While striving to rectify their past mistakes, the agents unravel a hidden conspiracy along the way.

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 3
programme.desc: Gambling tycoon Man suddenly marries his new partner Sophie, which shocked his only son, Ken. In the wake of Man's heart attack, Ken must battle Sophie - who has persuaded Man to transfer his grand master title to her in the event of his death - for the rightful claim to the familys gambling business in a riveting game of mahjong.

programme.title: The Hedgehog
programme.desc: Wang's odd behaviour and quirky ideas make him a social outcast. His teenage nephew Zhou, who is ashamed of his stutter, becomes Wang's only friend. Together, these misfits challenge traditional family expectations and social misunderstandings, supporting and inspiring each other as they seek their own paths in life.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Diary of a Lady-killer
programme.desc: Tycoon Zhou is a playboy who is engaged to be married, but that did not keep him from working his charms on as many ladies as he can. He keeps a diary about his romantic escapades and soon, the women with whom he has been intimate with are being murdered one by one. Zhou becomes the number one suspect by the police but is the killer someone else?

programme.title: The Villains
programme.desc: Hung is an orphan seeking help from her wealthy uncle who has two sons but only dotes on the younger son Feng, a playboy. Feng covets the beauty of Hung and rapes her but when she gets pregnant, Hung is wrongfully accused and gets sent off by her uncle to protect Feng. Will Feng be punished for his villainy?

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her sexy sister, and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: Four Riders
programme.desc: Four martial arts experts live in Seoul after the Korean War in the 1950s. One of them inexplicably crosses path with a drug trafficking syndicate, and his three friends have no choice but to fight a brutal battle on his side...

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bills nieces!

programme.title: Lady Of Steel
programme.desc: A young swordswoman Fang Ying Qi sets out to join the Flying Dragon Clan in their defense against the invading Jin forces. Fang also intends to avenge the murder of her parents by bandit leader Han 20 years ago. Han has since taken on a false identity as a member of the Flying Dragon Clan and Fang must rely on her deadly sword skills to stop Han.

programme.title: The Deadly Duo
programme.desc: The prince of the Sung Dynasty is captured by the Chin invaders and guarded by top martial arts masters. Two powerful patriots need to fight the overwhelming odds and pull off the impossible: to rescue the royal Prince and get out of the Chin stronghold alive.

programme.title: Rape of the Sword
programme.desc: The film starts out with two students fighting for their deceased master's sword called the "Green Frost Sword". Han kills the other student, takes the sword and offer it to the king. The wife of the other dead student plots to take revenge, going undercover to retrieve the sword at the first opportunity in this tale of revenge and betrayal.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: Illicit Desire
programme.desc: This instant cult classic adapts three erotic and mystical tales from the Chinese classical works, with stories spanning across time from the Tang to Ming dynasties. The stories, filled with characters such as emperors, concubines, monks and fortune-tellers, intertwine in a world of adultery, lust and greed, alongside great costumes!

programme.title: Marco Polo
programme.desc: Mongolian emperor Kublai Khan is being assassinated while meeting with the Italian explorer Marco Polo. Marco Polo is appointed to lead the troops for the emperor to wipe out the anti-Mongol rebels. Yet, he is touched by these rebels who are resisting the Mongolian invasion of their homeland. Will Marco Polo stay loyal to the emperor?

programme.title: The Daredevils
programme.desc: Corrupt general Wang Li assumes power by killing his superior. The son of the murdered superior befriends four street performers called The Venoms, and they help him take revenge by posing as government officials offering a peace token to the corrupt general. When Wang arrives at a warehouse, he is ambushed by the Venoms!

programme.title: The Tea House
programme.desc: Big Brother Cheng fled from the mainland to Hong Kong, where he opened a teahouse in a housing estate, hoping to find a peaceful life. However, relentless provocations from local triad gangs go unaddressed by the police, prompting Cheng and his friends at the teahouse to seek revenge.

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xus until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: The Magic Blade
programme.desc: The movie depicts Fu Hong Xue fighting against the formidable conspirator Master Yu and seeing through his deception. The brilliantly choreographed fights, glorious settings, superb cinematography and strong casts define this movie as a highpoint in Wu Xia cinema.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three sworn brothers, Zhang, Huang and Ma ends when Ma gives in to corruption and falls for Huang's wife, eventually leading to a bloody ending.

programme.title: The Tiger and the Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: The Secret Of The Dirk
programme.desc: The inhabitants of the City of Liu are forced to flee when the vicious Black Tigers gang raids their city, but are able to hide all their gold and treasures in a valley. A team of swordswomen led by Liu wants to get their hands on the treasures before the bandits, but both parties will have to contend with the wandering swordsman Chou for them...

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: To the tune of the Osmonds hit song, this is a story of adolescent playfulness & innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together and teasingly meet two delightfully impish boys leading to the four to flirtatiously intermingle. However, the innocence of partner swapping eventually leads to a roller-coaster bouts of misunderstood emotions.

programme.title: Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A Wu Dang disciple Fu, kills the chief of Wu Dang Clan and frames it on the chiefs illegitimate child, Yun. Fu then proclaims himself the new chief and orders the killing of Yun, who vows to avenge his fathers death and learns the invincible silkworm martial arts style in order to defeat Fu.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insiders look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiangs popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: The Proud Youth
programme.desc: Ling Hu Chong, a Huashan clans disciple, is assigned to find the successor to the score The Proud One. Ling identifies Ying for the score but finds out that she is the daughter of the evil clans leader. At the same time, he is unwittingly dragged into an epic power struggle between clans, with complicated allegiances and perplexing moralities.

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxus enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: The Imperial Tomb Raiders
programme.desc: The story revolves around a maverick, a band of woman warriors and a group of ruthless bandits. The maverick teams up with the woman warriors to battle the bandits seeking to raid the emperors tomb.

programme.title: The Twelve Gold Medallions
programme.desc: This was one of top three films of 1970 and winner of "Outstanding Drama" at the 9th Golden Horse Awards. The evil minister uses twelve golden medallions to summon war hero Yueh Fei back from the frontline and execute him. A group of wandering warriors, led by Yueh Hua and Chin Ping, try to stop the medallion couriers.

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Muis embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love

programme.title: The 14 Amazons
programme.desc: The Yang family had served their country in Song Dynasty for generations. When General Yang is ambushed and killed during the war in Jin Shan, the grand matriarch led the entire family to take revenge and defend the country.

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: This story has a Romeo and Juliet flavour. Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles and do not bother to have a bridge built. Their respective children meet in university and fall in love, but have to find ways to be together and resolve the hatred between their families.

programme.title: 7-Man Army
programme.desc: This iconoclastic film retells the legend of seven Chinese patriots, who sacrificed their lives to defend against 20,000 Japanese soldiers and 50 tanks for 5 days, at a strategic key point of the Great Wall known as Pa Tou Lou Tzu.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content; yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu Lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun Yang.

programme.title: The Magnificent Concubine
programme.desc: Yang Gui Fei is the beloved concubine of Emperor Tang Ming Huang, who is so besotted with her that he leaves the running of the country to Prime Minister Yang Guo Zhong, the brother of Yang Gui Fei. The Prime Minister is corrupt and cruel to the army, causing them to revolt and endanger the throne. Yang Gui Fei is also implicated and kills herself.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: Vengeance is a Golden Blade
programme.desc: Convoy Master Lis wife has an affair with his rival Long, who plans to steal Lis Golden Blade and kill him as well as his young daughter. Li and his daughter manage to escape and the latter grows up to be a skilled swordswoman who vows to avenge her mothers death a lie told by Li. The truth is revealed when she sees her mother alive by chance.

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Macro Worlds S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Meadow of Horror - It is horror! It is murder! Brutal death as well as exciting fights with an exceptional last-minute rescue. And after seeing it you will know the creepiest spot is actually the meadow in your neighborhood. With stylistic devices from the horror genre this extraordinary nature documentary takes you on a journey following a well-known hero with six legs, red wings and seven black dots through a seemingly normal meadow but full of monsters.

programme.title: Seasons of the Wild S1 Ep1
programme.desc: The Everglades: The Season of Drought - In Southern Florida, a unique and complex ecosystem known as the Everglades has entered its winter season. Predator and prey are forced to live in close proximity due to a limited supply of water.

programme.title: Life's Journey S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Life Begins - For the first few weeks of life, the world is a frightening place. Danger lurks around every corner. It pays to be alert. Whether predator or prey. Any day might be your last. The race is on to grow up fast- for even the largest animals are vulnerable to attack.

programme.title: Life's Journey S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Life's Lessons - If young animals survive until adulthood, the chances for survival are greatly increased - but many challenges face them before they can strike out on their own. Some have months to grow-up; other have decades but all, have lots to learn along the way. From getting to grips with their bodies and learning to feed themselves, to practicing fighting skills and learning how to form friendships. There are many hurdles along the way, but every small success could mean the difference between life and death.

programme.title: Life's Journey S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Life's Legacies - For every species on earth the right to mate is the purpose of life. Passing on your genes to the next generation is every animals legacy. But its not easy, it can be a struggle to find a mate and then a fight to gain access. Only the strongest and most determined will win at Luangwas mating game.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Koala S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Koala Country - Despite being one of Australias best-known marsupials, koalas live only in the east and southeast parts of the continent. Learn how their lives and behaviors vary in these different regions.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Koala S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Breeding Season - Koalas may seem solitary and inert, but mating season brings a dramatic shift in their behavior, leading to movement, contact, and conflict. As breeding season begins, follow two large males on a mission to mate.

programme.title: Brazil Untamed S1 Ep10
programme.desc: The Pantanal - The Pantanal experiences extreme climatic shifts, from brutal droughts during the searingly hot dry season to floods created by rainy-season tempests. See how the regions diverse animal population works to coexist and ensure collective survival.

programme.title: Rooted S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Memoirs of Acacia - Across rippled dunes, in the wind-swept grasslands of the southern Kalahari towers a magnificent Camelthorn. It has stood here for two centuries. This tree is never lonely, learn how it provides food, shelter and a hunting ground to many creatures.

programme.title: Rooted S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Sweet Seduction - Discover the story of the much loved Sausage Tree, whose nectar filled blooms and sausage shaped fruits entice animals of all kinds, from insects to elephants. See how the very animals who rely on this generous tree ensure its proliferation.
